  "remarks": "\nHamed Abdollahi is a senior commander in the Iranian Revolutionary Guards-Qods Force (IRGC-QF). Mr Abdollahi has been accused of overseeing and coordinating the attempted assassination of Adel al-Jubeir, the Saudi ambassador to the US, in 2011.\n",
